-- MOVES-SEI names director of its London institutional group
-- 
-- Thu Jul 31, 2014 07:30AM EDT
-- None



July 31 (Reuters) - SEI Investments Co <SEIC.O> named Paul Nevin as director of the company's institutional group based in London.

Nevin joins from Credit Suisse <CSGN.VX> where he was managing director of structured solutions. Prior to that role, Nevin worked at Towers Watson & Co <TW.N> as a senior investment consultant.